title: How To: Replace RPWFE Water Filter in GE Fridge
description:
How To: Replace RPWFE Water Filter on GE Refrigerator 

Buy The GE RPWFE Water Filter At Abt: 
http://www.abt.com/product/88616/GE-RPWFE.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=RPWFE_20160203

- Locate filter inside the upper left of the unit 
- Press with thumb and slide pointer finger behind compartment and pull
- Pull filter to side and pull out
- Filter is marked so please follow instructions
- Push into the guide and push into slot 
- Close compartment
